OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,6,Fband clears south by Monday evening,
OL,7,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Cloudier
OL,8,FTuesday with outbreaks of rain.
OL,9,FWednesday starts off dry with heavy
OL,10,Fshowers developing later.
